'''Poltroop''' was a plant native to [[Gamorr/Legends|Gamorr]]. It was used by the [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] to weave baskets and the seeds were pressed to extract an [[Poltroop-oil seed|oil]] that was burned for light and heat.

